Mac-MotionSensor version 0.01 
=============================

Provides an interface to the accelerometer available in mac laptops

CREDIT

Thanks to those responsible for the unimotion framework, this module simply wraps there API

http://unimotion.sourceforge.net/

ISSUES

Known not to work under x86_64, its an issue with the unimotion library.

On Mac OS X 10.6 it will build under system perl 5.8.9.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  xCode must be installed

http://developer.apple.com/technologies/tools/xcode.html 

